&quot;Behind you.&quot; &quot;Dont turn and keep your back to me.&quot;<br>
Demosae bows his head under his cloak not to reveal his identity.<br>
&quot;I heard on the street something was going down. Alot of shady characters have been showing up like there was some kinda convention. As tight lipped as some are the rumors are the OBR is in town. Is that much true?&quot;<br>
Demosae grabs the his informants hand and drops a few gold in it.<br>
&quot;Hmm. I see. When and where?&quot;<br>
The man says nothing cups his hand for another deposit.<br>
&quot;Ha, one payment was always good enough between us old friend. But alas the times are harsh and I am more then happy to give what you deserve.&quot;<br>
With that Demosae grabs his middle finger and with his dagger puts its point just deep enough to draw blood from the mans palm.<br>
&quot;Need I ask again, dear friend? No, I thought not. Tell me what you know or all the gold in the land shall fall through your hand, for good.&quot;<br>
The blood begins to drip quite rapidly to the ground.<br>
&quot;Well, I see. I may need to attend this &quot;gathering&quot; wont I. Thank you my friend. You are truely a master at your craft.&quot;<br>
The man nods his head, while holding his hand to his chest, and bids Demosae fair well as old friends do. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
