</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uinkelongdirk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Inke Longdirk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 235<br> <font color=#9C0000>(3/21/01 4:47:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fsbobrfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=48.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/madmarty28/black.html height=100 width=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Meeting in the Shadows</span><hr size=1> As Demosae steps out of site, another figure emerges from the shadows in front of the man. His face also concealed in the hood of his cloak.<br>
<br>
In a flash, he grasps the informants throat so he cannot make a sound and pins the already bleeding hand to the wall with a dagger, seemingly appearing out of thin air.<br>
<br>
He leans towards the man and whispers in his ear &quot;This is dangerous information you have. Who else have you told? Where did you hear it? I will know if you lie, and if you do, you will die tonight&quot;<br>
<br>
As he loosens his grip, the wild eyed informant quickly answers. <br>
<br>
&quot;You have been honest with me, and it has saved your life. But make no mistake, I would have taken it had I not heard Demosae speak of you as a long time associate. If I had seen you giving this information to anyone other than a possible ally, you cannot imagine the suffering you would have faced.&quot;<br>
<br>
As quickly as the dagger appeared, it vanishes into the folds of the strangers cloak as he fades into the shadows.<br>
<br>
The terrified man stares in disbelief into the shadows where he can see no trace of the cloaked figure who was there moments before. He hears the voice again, now from behind &quot;Tell no one of our business again. If you wish to sell information. You will sell it to us.&quot;<br>
<br>
The man realizes he has been face to face with a Rose and lived. As he looks down to his mangled hand, he sees a black rose in his bloody palm. He stares at the rose and doesn't move for a very long time.<br>
